com.foreach.across.modules.webcms.domain.component.model.create

Class WebCmsComponentAutoCreateQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.webcms.domain.component.model.create.WebCmsComponentAutoCreateQueue

  • @Component
 @Exposed
 @Scope(value="request",
       proxyMode=TARGET_CLASS)
public class WebCmsComponentAutoCreateQueue
extends Object
    Represents the request-bound queue for auto-creation of components. Used by template parsers to signal to manage the actual component rendering blocks.
    Since:
    0.0.2
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
